column4: I reinstalled recently, and just brought over my backed up .gnupg folder into my fresh home folder. This results in the complete key being visible in Seahorse, but I don't have an encrypt/decrypt option in Nautilus. Why?

i use sbackup but it doesnt work and i donw know what other alternatives there are or how to backup by using gui only
